                <h2 data-aos="fade-up" class="text-white h2 text-center mb-2">The program</h2>
                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="text-white body--sm text-center px-0 px-sm-3">
                    42 is a future-proof computer science training to educate the next generation of software engineers. The 42 program takes a project-based approach to progress and is designed to develop technical and people skills that match the expectations of the labor market.</p>
                                <ul class="icons-container d-flex justify-content-around flex-wrap">
                                        
                    <li data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200"
